8:["$","section",null,{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__section","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__container","children":[["$","div","0",{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__textBlock","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__subTitle","children":"Why Resurface with the TimberTech Vintage Collection"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__paragraph","children":["The TimberTech Vintage Collection is the gold standard of composite decking in the industry. While many homeowners are familiar with standard composite boards, Vintage stands apart by utilizing an Advanced PVC material core that contains zero wood fibers. This makes it a superior option compared to traditional ",["$","$L16","312",{"href":"/services/new-decks","children":"new deck construction"}]," materials."]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__paragraph","children":["This 100% synthetic composition makes it effectively immune to the moisture, swelling, mold, and rot that slowly degrades traditional wood-composite blends in Northern Virginia's humid climate. Its proprietary capping technology resists fading and staining, ensuring your deck looks as vibrant in year 20 as it did on day one."]}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__detailsList","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__listItem","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":["Unmatched Aesthetics",":"]}]," ",["Wire-brushed texture that perfectly mimics the intricate grain patterns of premium hardwood."]]}],["$","li","1",{"className":"ServiceContentExpansion-module__6_-y9q__listItem","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":["Advanced PVC Core",":"]}]," ",["Zero organic material means zero food source for mold, mildew, or termites."]]}],["$","li","2",{"className